{"tid":389862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中環·李祖祺醫生好唔好㗎？","createTime":"2017-09-06T15:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T15:17:35.000Z","uid":141997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6659d4a9e89c03e429cc76dd885dfe0ad36b1f","tid":389862,"uid":141997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:17:35.000Z","msg":"話說今日去咗中環睇李祖祺皮膚科醫生，因小弟面部暗瘡都幾嚴重下（都有幾年）！想改善一下皮膚！<br />\n但嗰個醫生睇唔夠2分鐘就睇完仲俾左一張紙仔我係關於皮膚護理用品中心，聽講佢老婆開！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入嚟大家分享下依間野得唔得！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/231715_bc07b68608941ae922152cb8ceadb821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F231715_bc07b68608941ae922152cb8ceadb821.jpg&h=8ffa91c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/231715_568d83d89c40094da5268e2c7f8b2e36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F231715_568d83d89c40094da5268e2c7f8b2e36.jpg&h=ad3c323a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}